---
title: Smart Tuscan-Inspired Creamy Double Chicken Soup with Garlic Toast
description: It's hard to improve on perfection, like a bowl of homemade chicken soup, but we certainly can try. Creamy and savoury, this dish nods to the Tuscan countryside with some sun-dried tomato pesto and is served up with some garlic toast!
